**Important Dates - Fall 2022 Capstone Projects**

~~**August 29, 2022** - Fall Semester Starts - Teams and faculty advisors meet this week. Teams must schedule a “kick-off meeting” with the client by Friday, September2nd. 

**September 22–23, September 26-28; 12pm-1:20pm** – Midterm Practice Sessions with Program Director, Dean Wasser, David Riel, Chris Labash, andother Heinz attendees. Teams can sign up for a day and time here.

**October 10, 2022 – October 31, 2022** - Midterm Presentations – Time slots will be between 7:50am-5:10pm; specific dates and times are coordinated between teams and sponsors and can be scheduled here.~~
 
**November 18, 2022; 12pm-1:20pm** - Creative Video Information Session with Program Director, Dean Wasser, David Riel, Chris Labash, and other Heinz attendees.

**December 5, 2022** – Creative Videos due by Noon. Individual team box files to submit videos will be sent out closer to date.  

**December 12, 2022 - December 16, 2022** - Final Presentations - Time slots will be between 7:50am-5:10pm; specific dates and times are coordinated between teams and sponsors and can be scheduled here.

**December 19, 2022** - Final report, peer reviews, and faculty evaluations due by Noon.
